object.customQuery:
with current_batch as (
select
	bls.batch_id,
	bls.source_start_cutoff_datetime,
	bls.source_end_cutoff_datetime
from
	$$operational_schema.batch_load_summary bls
where
	bls.source_system_code = '$$sourcesystemcode'
	and bls.batch_status = 'Inprogress'
	and bls.batch_id = (
	select
		MAX(batch_id)
	from
		$$operational_schema.batch_load_summary
	where
		source_system_code = '$$sourcesystemcode'
		and batch_status = 'Inprogress'
      )
)	
	
	select
	distinct
TRIM(metal_ascea.source_name) as source_name,
TRIM(metal_ascea.load_type) as load_type,
TRIM(metal_ascea.system_id) as system_id,
TRIM(metal_ascea.parent_id) as parent_id,
TRIM(metal_ascea.cmm_container) as cmm_container,
TRIM(metal_ascea.id) as id,
TRIM(metal_ascea.search_criteria_name) as search_criteria_name,
TRIM(metal_ascea.search_criteria_value) as search_criteria_value,
TRIM(metal_ascea.type) as type,
TRIM(metal_ascea.key_parent_bean_ref_id) as key_parent_bean_ref_id,
CAST(TRIM(metal_ascea.row_id) AS BIGINT) AS row_id,
current_batch.batch_id as batch_id
from
	$$raw_schema.acx_search_criteria_ea metal_ascea
cross join current_batch
order by
	metal_ascea.system_id,
metal_ascea.id,
metal_ascea.cmm_container;

attributes.name: Download S3 Files In Multiple Parts

object.customQuery:
select DISTINCT
	system_id,
	cmm_container,
	id,
	row_id,
	acx_search_criteria_ea_row_id,
	acx_search_criteria_ea_row_md5checksum,
	acx_search_criteria_ea_row_effective_end_datetime
from
	$$staging_schema.acx_search_criteria_ea
where
	acx_search_criteria_ea_row_effective_end_datetime = '9999-12-31 00:00:00.000'
order by system_id, cmm_container,id;
